SAPS and Reaction Unit SA are requesting the public to be on the lookout for 26-year old Joel Pillay who is missing from his Bottlebrush Road home in Chatsworth since Friday, November 6, 2015.According to Sergeant K Padayachee was last seen in seen in the vicinity of Crossmoor (Unit 11) between 9 and 10am on Friday. Joel was driving a black VW Golf with registration NX 30430 at the time of his disappearance. His phone has been off ever since, said Padayachee.If you have any information on Joel Pillay&#8217;s whereabouts or spot his vehicle then please contact Reaction Unit South Africa on 0861234333 or Sergeant K. Padayachee on 0798793602.